{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/mengenal-sosok-penting-desainer-hardware-nintendo-genyo-takeda/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Mengenal Sosok Penting Desainer Hardware Nintendo: Genyo Takeda","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Video game tidak pernah lepas dari yang namanya “design/desain”. Karena desain memegang peranan kunci untuk video game agar menarik saat dilihat, dimainkan maupun didengar. Desain yang bagus akan menjadikan sebuah video game menarik. Karena itulah sosok-sosok desainer video game seperti misalnya Hideo Kojima (Metal Gear series) atau Cory Barlog (God of War series) merupakan tokoh penting dan berpengaruh di industri video game saat ini. Game-game mereka seru untuk dimainkan dengan grafis-gameplay-musik yang menarik. Semua karena berasal dari desain mereka. Desain yang membuat video game jadi seperti yang kita nikmati melalui console, PC maupun handheld.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44030\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44030\" data-attachment-id=\"44030\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengenal-sosok-penting-desainer-hardware-nintendo-genyo-takeda/attachment/nintendohardware7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Hideo Kojima &#038; Norman Reedus. Sumber gambar: polygon.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Hideo Kojima &#038; Norman Reedus. Sumber gambar: polygon.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44030\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware7.jpg\" alt=\"Hideo Kojima &amp; Norman Reedus. Sumber gambar: polygon.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44030\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hideo Kojima &amp; Norman Reedus. Sumber gambar: polygon.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tapi sehebat apapun desain para desainer video game tadi, mereka tetap perlu platform. Perlu tempat. Dan walaupun semua pembuatan video game dilakukan melalui medium seragam (alias komputer), tapi ujung-ujungnya game akan dimainkan di luar dari komputer. Misalnya di console game. Dan disinilah fungsi dari sosok penting lainnya dari sebuah video game yang kita nikmati itu: yaitu desainer hardware.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44038\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44038\" data-attachment-id=\"44038\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengenal-sosok-penting-desainer-hardware-nintendo-genyo-takeda/attachment/nintendoharware4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendoharware4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"nintendoharware4\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Gaming consoles. Sumber gambar: engadget&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendoharware4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendoharware4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44038\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendoharware4.jpg\" alt=\"Gaming consoles. Sumber gambar: engadget\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendoharware4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendoharware4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44038\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gaming consoles. Sumber gambar: engadget</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Genyo Takeda adalah satu dari sedikit tokoh penting desainer hardware video game dunia.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44028\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44028\" data-attachment-id=\"44028\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengenal-sosok-penting-desainer-hardware-nintendo-genyo-takeda/attachment/nintendohardware5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Genyo Takeda saat memperkenalkan Nintendo GameCube. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Genyo Takeda saat memperkenalkan Nintendo GameCube. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44028\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware5.jpg\" alt=\"Genyo Takeda saat memperkenalkan Nintendo GameCube. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44028\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Genyo Takeda saat memperkenalkan Nintendo GameCube. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Takeda, yang berusia 68 tahun, baru saja pensiun tahun 2017 lalu dari Nintendo, tempatnya bekerja sejak era 70an. Pencapaian Takeda di industri video game tidak dapat dianggap kecil. Beliau merupakan tokoh dibalik desain-desain hardware Nintedo yang ikonik. Seperti contohnya “battery backup” di cartridge Famicom/NES. Dengan mekanisme battery backup ini, game NES memungkinkan untuk melakukan proses ‘save file’ yang tentu saja berguna untuk gamers pada masa itu. Sehingga jika seseorang bermain game yang panjang (seperti misalnya RPG), mereka bisa menyimpan proses permainan mereka untuk nanti dilanjutkan kembali lain waktu. Generasi 90an mengenali proses ini lewat “memory card” seperti yang dipopulerkan Sony PlayStation One.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44032\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44032\" data-attachment-id=\"44032\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengenal-sosok-penting-desainer-hardware-nintendo-genyo-takeda/attachment/nintendohardware9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sebelum era Memory Card dan HDD Save. Sumber gambar: dkoldies.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sebelum era Memory Card dan HDD Save. Sumber gambar: dkoldies.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware9.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44032\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware9.jpg\" alt=\"Sebelum era Memory Card dan HDD Save. Sumber gambar: dkoldies.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44032\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sebelum era Memory Card dan HDD Save. Sumber gambar: dkoldies.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Takeda dan team desainer Nintendo juga menciptakan stick analog untuk console Nintendo 64 yang memorable itu. Bro sis pernah lihat joystick Nintendo 64? Bentuknya sekilas terlihat aneh dan lucu, tapi begitu berada dalam genggaman joystick itu akan terasa berguna banget; terutama dengan kemampuan ‘tiga model pegangan’ nya yang unik bahkan untuk ukuran masa kini.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44034\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44034\" data-attachment-id=\"44034\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengenal-sosok-penting-desainer-hardware-nintendo-genyo-takeda/attachment/nintendohardware11/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware11.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Desain yang unik dan tidak orthodox. Sumber gambar: wikipedia.org\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Desain yang unik dan tidak orthodox. Sumber gambar: wikipedia.org&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware11-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware11.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44034\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware11.jpg\" alt=\"Desain yang unik dan tidak orthodox. Sumber gambar: wikipedia.org\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware11.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware11-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44034\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Desain yang unik dan tidak orthodox. Sumber gambar: wikipedia.org</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_44033\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44033\" data-attachment-id=\"44033\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengenal-sosok-penting-desainer-hardware-nintendo-genyo-takeda/attachment/nintendohardware10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware10.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tiga cara pakai joystick Nintendo 64. Sumber gambar: nintendo.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tiga cara pakai joystick Nintendo 64. Sumber gambar: nintendo.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware10-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware10.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44033\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware10.jpg\" alt=\"Tiga cara pakai joystick Nintendo 64. Sumber gambar: nintendo.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware10.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware10-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44033\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tiga cara pakai joystick Nintendo 64. Sumber gambar: nintendo.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dan jangan lupakan gimana unik/nyentrik/aneh/absurd nya controller Nintendo Wii, the Wiimote &amp; Nunchuk. Ini juga merupakan karya Genyo Takeda yang ikonik banget. Takeda saat itu berpendapat kalau “sebuah konsol game tidak harus punya kemampuan proses dan grafis sangat tinggi untuk dapat sukses”. Beliau menganalogikan hal ini dengan “lihat saja mobil keluarga dengan mobil sport, siapa yang lebih laku di pasaran”.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44036\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44036\" data-attachment-id=\"44036\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengenal-sosok-penting-desainer-hardware-nintendo-genyo-takeda/attachment/nintendohardware19/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware19.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Joystick unik untuk gamers Wii. Sumber gambar: crazysales.com.au\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Joystick unik untuk gamers Wii. Sumber gambar: crazysales.com.au&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware19-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware19.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44036\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware19.jpg\" alt=\"Joystick unik untuk gamers Wii. Sumber gambar: crazysales.com.au\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware19.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware19-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44036\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Joystick unik untuk gamers Wii. Sumber gambar: crazysales.com.au</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Konsep pemikiran itu terbukti di Wii. Walaupun kalah “otot” dibandingkan dua kompetitornya saat itu (PlayStation 3 &amp; Xbox 360), tapi Wii tetap sukses laku terjual banyak bahkan hingga melebihi angka 100 juta unit selama masa hidupnya di pasaran.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Di kalangan internal Nintendo sendiri, Genyo Takeda adalah sosok yang dihormati &amp; disegani berbagai lintas generasi desainer. “Dulu sekali, Takeda-san membuat game arcade berjudul EVR Race” terang desainer <i>high-tier</i> Nintendo yang dikenal luas sebagai pencipta Mario dan banyak game Nintendo lainnya, Shigeru Miyamoto, di acara “Iwata’s Ask” tahun 2009. EVR Race sendiri adalah game arcade balapan kuda dengan 6 pemain yang dirilis Nintendo tahun 1975. “EVR Race adalah video game pertama yang Nintendo ciptakan” sambung Shigeru Miyamoto kemudian.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44041\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44041\" data-attachment-id=\"44041\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengenal-sosok-penting-desainer-hardware-nintendo-genyo-takeda/attachment/re3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/re3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Mesin arcade/video game/betting machine pertama Nintendo. Sumber gambar: tvtropes.org\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Mesin arcade/video game/betting machine pertama Nintendo. Sumber gambar: tvtropes.org&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/re3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/re3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44041\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/re3.jpg\" alt=\"Mesin arcade/video game/betting machine pertama Nintendo. Sumber gambar: tvtropes.org\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/re3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/re3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44041\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mesin arcade/video game/betting machine pertama Nintendo. Sumber gambar: tvtropes.org</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Game arcade lain ciptaan Genyo Takeda adalah game tinju fenomenal “Punch-Out!!” tahun 1983. Game ini juga unik karena menggunakan dua layar ketimbang satu; sesuatu yang tidak biasa pada masa itu.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44035\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44035\" data-attachment-id=\"44035\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengenal-sosok-penting-desainer-hardware-nintendo-genyo-takeda/attachment/nintendohardware12/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tampil beda dengan dua layar. Sumber gambar: alchetron.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tampil beda dengan dua layar. Sumber gambar: alchetron.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware12-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware12.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44035\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware12.jpg\" alt=\"Tampil beda dengan dua layar. Sumber gambar: alchetron.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware12.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware12-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44035\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tampil beda dengan dua layar. Sumber gambar: alchetron.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">“Untuk Wii, kami bisa saja mencoba memompa kemampuan console itu agar memiliki tampilan grafis yang lebih tinggi lagi dari kompetitor kami saat itu” kata Genyo Takeda saat ditanya soal mengapa Wii tidak memiliki kemampuan grafis sama/melebihi PS3 ataupun X360 yang merupakan kompetitor utama mereka.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">“Tapi saat developing mesin tersebut kami bertanya-tanya apakah grafis tinggi memang jadi tujuan utama konsumen kami? Dalam perjalanannya kami melihat kalau kami bisa tetap memberikan kualitas gaming Nintendo seperti yang diharapkan fans tanpa harus menaikkan biaya produksi (karena penambahan kualitas grafis) dan memberikan sesuatu yang fresh dengan joystick Wiimote + Nunchuk” sambung Takeda lagi.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44042\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44042\" data-attachment-id=\"44042\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengenal-sosok-penting-desainer-hardware-nintendo-genyo-takeda/attachment/re13/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/re13.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Kualitas grafis Wii tidak istimewa. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kualitas grafis Wii tidak istimewa. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/re13-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/re13.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44042\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/re13.jpg\" alt=\"Kualitas grafis Wii tidak istimewa. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/re13.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/re13-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44042\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kualitas grafis Wii tidak istimewa. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Atas berbagai pencapaiannya di Nintendo hingga pensiun, Genyo Takeda dianugerahi penghargaan “Lifetime Achievement Award” oleh The Academy of Interactive Arts &amp; Sciences (AIAS) di tahun 2018 pada acara 21<sup>st</sup> D.I.C.E Awards tanggal 22 February di Las Vegas, Amerika Serikat. Mendiang Satoru Iwata dari Nintendo juga merupakan penerima penghargaan yang sama sebelumnya selain tokoh-tokoh penting industri video game dunia seperti Howard Lincoln dan “bapaknya PlayStation” Ken Kutaragi.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44031\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44031\" data-attachment-id=\"44031\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengenal-sosok-penting-desainer-hardware-nintendo-genyo-takeda/attachment/nintendohardware8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Ex-CEO Sony Kaz Hirai &#038; pencipta PlayStation Ken Kutaragi. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Ex-CEO Sony Kaz Hirai &#038; pencipta PlayStation Ken Kutaragi. Sumber gambar: kotaku.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/nintendohardware8.jpg\" class=\"